service: python-lambda-api


provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: python3.9
  region: us-west-2
  memorySize: 128
  timeout: 10
  iam:
    role:
      statements:
        - Effect: Allow
          Action:
            - s3:GetObject
            - s3:PutObject
            - s3:DeleteObject
            - s3:ListBucket
          Resource:
            - arn:aws:s3:::putest-tfstate
            - arn:aws:s3:::putest-tfstate/*
  

functions:
  helloworld:
    handler: helloworld/main.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: hello
          method: get
          cors: true
  list_s3:
    handler: list_s3/main.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: list_s3
          method: get
          cors: true
